I hope I'll not
be eating long at your
expense, Mr. Rivers.

109
00:13:16,880 --> 00:13:18,079
Then tell me where
to place you.

110
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:21,039
Show me where to seek
work, that is all I ask.

111
