How do you do,
my dear?

222
00:24:20,360 --> 00:24:22,479
Are you Mrs. Fairfax?
Indeed I am

223
00:24:26,560 --> 00:24:29,039
What a tedious journey
you must have had.

224
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:31,559
Your hands must
be frozen. Here.

225
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:39,039
Goodness.
How young you are.

226
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:41,359
I'm quite experienced
I can assure you

227
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:44,879
Of course you are.
I'm sure we're very
lucky to have you.

228
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:47,959
Leah, would you
ask Martha to bring
a little hot port

229
00:24:48,080 --> 00:24:49,439
and cut a sandwich or two?

230
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:51,159
Draw nearer the fire

231
